41
00:05:27,490 --> 00:05:30,220
SPEAKER_16: Master Fugui is going home. You take him.

140
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:47,769
SPEAKER_16: I am very sorry, but you've got nothing left.

141
00:14:48,049 --> 00:14:51,779
SPEAKER_16: What could you stake the bet on?
We don't accept empty bets.

151
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:31,649
SPEAKER_16: Your wife's been waiting for ages.

163
00:17:30,210 --> 00:17:32,400
SPEAKER_16: Mr. Xu, any mistakes?

289
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,220
SPEAKER_16: The wounded who froze to death.

301
00:33:58,930 --> 00:34:00,589
SPEAKER_16: They've all run off.

302
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:02,130
SPEAKER_16: How could that be?

313
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,460
SPEAKER_16: So, no running?

778
01:27:58,970 --> 01:28:00,869
SPEAKER_16: Comrade Wan Erxi.

822
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:38,449
SPEAKER_16: We must be going.

829
01:32:01,979 --> 01:32:04,810
SPEAKER_16: Thanks, we'll go to the factory bathhouse.

863
01:36:16,430 --> 01:36:17,989
SPEAKER_16: Chairman Mao...

864
01:36:18,869 --> 01:36:21,600
SPEAKER_16: Comrade Fengxia's mine now.

1042
01:50:52,210 --> 01:50:54,829
SPEAKER_16: Do as Mommy says and push.

1043
01:50:54,909 --> 01:50:56,640
SPEAKER_16: Everything will be fine.

1078
01:53:31,029 --> 01:53:33,159
SPEAKER_16: We dragged him here today...

1079
01:53:33,300 --> 01:53:36,270
SPEAKER_16: to educate him, to criticize him...

1080
01:53:37,340 --> 01:53:39,899
SPEAKER_16: and to let him witness her giving birth.

1081
01:53:39,970 --> 01:53:42,909
SPEAKER_16: To show him the heirs
of this new, Red world.

1086
01:54:03,300 --> 01:54:05,289
SPEAKER_16: That's professor Wang...

1087
01:54:05,500 --> 01:54:07,229
SPEAKER_16: head of obstetrics.

1088
01:54:15,010 --> 01:54:17,029
SPEAKER_16: Dr. Wang, don't be afraid.

1150
01:59:11,869 --> 01:59:13,460
SPEAKER_16: - Have a look.
- Not yet!

1158
01:59:35,359 --> 01:59:37,689
SPEAKER_16: Erxi, you're a lucky man!

1166
02:00:00,789 --> 02:00:02,380
SPEAKER_16: What's with him?

1167
02:00:11,630 --> 02:00:13,390
SPEAKER_16: He ate too quickly.

1195
02:02:18,619 --> 02:02:20,680
SPEAKER_16: Never mind. Drag him over!

1196
02:02:21,489 --> 02:02:23,720
SPEAKER_16: She's bleeding! Quick!

1253
02:07:11,979 --> 02:07:13,350
SPEAKER_16: It's okay.

1262
02:07:42,550 --> 02:07:44,180
SPEAKER_16: Not just buns...

1263
02:07:44,279 --> 02:07:46,310
SPEAKER_16: anything made from wheat.

